3. In the Search box type the name of the browser to open, in this image **chrome** has been typed. *- red circle*
4. Click the **App** button **Google Chrome App**. *- yellow circle*

| Search text | Browser app name |
| ------------- | -------------- |
| chrome | Google Chrome |
| edge | Microsoft Edge |
| firefox | Firefox |
| brave | Brave |
| opera | Opera |

*If the button **App** is not shown, the browser is not installed or the text typed doesn't match the App name.*

